 class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e5c4bb75d4e68d95ff57406a31c7cd40450a57","tid":1075394,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T09:41:09.000Z","msg":"宜家得閒，認真回<br />\n<br />\n你係用咩 filter paper，咩磨豆機<br />\n沖煮既過程係點樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n盡量描述得仔細啲，或者可以幫助你提升技巧改善味道<br />\n<br />\n但應該唔會提升到好多<br />\n因為啲豆都未必係好靚既豆<br />\n抱住唔好浪費既心態去諗點改善味道<br />\n都算係對於環保既一種支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cab6ba4cd9c6f58bd79aece618a897a908ae934","tid":1075394,"uid":176553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:31:44.000Z","msg":"街飲係espresso加熱水變Americano/long black，espresso加奶加朱古力拉花就唔討論，因為唔係齋啡同手沖冇關。街都有手沖，佢地會叫手工咖啡，好撚貴一杯。磨豆自己沖化算好多。"},{"pid":"4514626889686fccc6f90fba7f57fe9afae21344","tid":1075394,"uid":176553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4885536a8af23a35026f9c6c636745e54c9b87d1","tid":1075394,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e75220046961aa98d927ac9ba3d52b8294bfddb7","tid":1075394,"uid":227992,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8a7bdf8ac0d815a5ba643c3decb1c24c7e52a9e1","tid":1075394,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T08:53:41.000Z","msg":"有，甚至覺得幼得滯，下次試試磨返粗少少"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T08:55:58.000Z","msg":"應該唔關事，要壓一壓下，壓到仲有位可以加粉，味道會濃d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T09:37:49.000Z","msg":"你唔好玩鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢講緊壓一壓粉應該係espresso maker，個粉要好幼，出黎係espresso，唔關手沖事。<br />\n<br />\nfrench presser就熱水浸住咖啡粉，要粗d先可以好發。太幼會好似泥漿咁。<br />\n<br />\nPour over/dripper 加filter應該係樓主果種，太幼粉都變泥漿咁發唔起。由中到粗都可以試，唔同水溫又會唔同味。"},{"pid":"4119fa4f8da651f2ad41fc66f3a9bddf8301332f","tid":1075394,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86e5c4bb75d4e68d95ff57406a31c7cd40450a57","tid":1075394,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T09:41:09.000Z","msg":"宜家得閒，認真回<br />\n<br />\n你係用咩 filter paper，咩磨豆機<br />\n沖煮既過程係點樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n盡量描述得仔細啲，或者可以幫助你提升技巧改善味道<br />\n<br />\n但應該唔會提升到好多<br />\n因為啲豆都未必係好靚既豆<br />\n抱住唔好浪費既心態去諗點改善味道<br />\n都算係對於環保既一種支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T16:18:43.000Z","msg":"佢瑪莎買架咋d豆咁認真把撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb59225cf2160913674a048e3ceec8a37d53a087","tid":1075394,"uid":96708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T16:21:30.000Z","msg":"去d有炒豆既coffe shop買新鮮豆啦，兩個境界黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e452206ddc0966e63548ea78ef0150e69749500","tid":1075394,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4119fa4f8da651f2ad41fc66f3a9bddf8301332f","tid":1075394,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86e5c4bb75d4e68d95ff57406a31c7cd40450a57","tid":1075394,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T09:41:09.000Z","msg":"宜家得閒，認真回<br />\n<br />\n你係用咩 filter paper，咩磨豆機<br />\n沖煮既過程係點樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n盡量描述得仔細啲，或者可以幫助你提升技巧改善味道<br />\n<br />\n但應該唔會提升到好多<br />\n因為啲豆都未必係好靚既豆<br />\n抱住唔好浪費既心態去諗點改善味道<br />\n都算係對於環保既一種支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T16:18:43.000Z","msg":"佢瑪莎買架咋d豆咁認真把撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T17:39:15.000Z","msg":"支持環保嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好過掉落海呀，好似係"},{"pid":"d65766f814cff1b05f0e5c5d4e5cdf0fe79716e8","tid":1075394,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:15:09.000Z","msg":"我用nanopresso, 有16 BAR壓力。 用HARIO磨啲豆ground到好幼，沖出黎好黑好多creamer. 啲渣變泥醬，如果用買返黎啲粉(粗啲)沖會好硬。"}]}